reviews.review_text: OFF THE CHART ROW JIMMY the audience clapped in succession from the floor to the top seats and back- It was WILD. Then when the band left for intermission there was a faint hell in a bucket playing - once acknowledged as Hell in a Bucket - you could hear the audience realizing the song- Crazy show- I definate head treat! For me anyway!
First Show I was there. My first show. Garcia stepped back going into the first solo and gave a little kick. The place erupted.
